ex := 1/(x*sqrt(x^n-a^n))
normalize(D(aa.1,x)-ex)
normalize(D(aa.2,x)-ex)

both return 0. Also

expRule := rule %e^(n*log x) == x^n
(20) -> expRule normalize(bb-aa.2)

