(%i4) (2*atan(sqrt(x^n-a^n)/a^(n/2)))/(a^(n/2)*n)$
(%i5) ratsimp(diff(%,x));
(%o5) 1/(x*sqrt(x^n-a^n))

Barton



so Maxima is not wrong.

